quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"ql -ayha alrswl-: awha allah 'ily ann jamaeat min aljini qad aistamaeuu ltlawty llqran, falamaa smewh qaluu lqwmhm: 'iinaa samiena qranana bdyeana fi blaghth wfsahth whkmh wahkamh wakhbarh, yadeu 'iilaa alhaqi walhda, fsddaqna bhdha alquran wemlna bh, walan nushrik birabina aldhy khalaqna ahdana fi ebadth"
  72,2,"ql -ayha alrswl-: awha allah 'ily ann jamaeat min aljini qad aistamaeuu ltlawty llqran, falamaa smewh qaluu lqwmhm: 'iinaa samiena qranana bdyeana fi blaghth wfsahth whkmh wahkamh wakhbarh, yadeu 'iilaa alhaqi walhda, fsddaqna bhdha alquran wemlna bh, walan nushrik birabina aldhy khalaqna ahdana fi ebadth"
  72,3,"wanh tealat ezmt rabana wjlalh, ma atakhadh zawjat wala wldana"
  72,4,"wan sfyhna- wahu 'iblys- kan yaqul ealaa allah taealaa qawlana beydana ean alhaqu walswab, min daewaa alsahbt walwld"
  72,5,"wanna hasibna 'ana ahdana ln yukadhib ealaa allah teala, la min al'iins wala min aljini fi nisbat alsahbt walwld 'ilyh"
  72,6,"wanh kan rijal min al'iins ystjyrwn birijal min aljn, fzad rjal aljnn al'ins basteadhthm bihim khwfana w'irhabana wrebana. whdhh alasteadht bighayr allh, alty neaha allah ela ahl aljahlyt, min alshirk alakbr, aldhy la yghfrh allah 'iilaa baltwbt alnswh mnh. wafi alayat tahdhir shadid min alluju' 'iilaa alsaharat walmshewdhyn washbahhm"
  72,7,wan kafaar al'iins hsbu kama hsbtm- ya maeshar aljn- 'ana allah taealaa lan yabeath ahdana baed almwt
  72,8,"wanna- maeshar aljn- talabna bulugh alsma'; lastmae kalam ahlha, fawajadnaha mulyt bialmalayikat alkathirin aladhin yhrswnha, wbalshhb almahraqat alty yurma biha man yaqtarib mnha"
  72,9,"wana kunaa qabl dhlk natakhidh min alsama' mwade; lnstme 'iilaa akhbarha, faman yuhawil alan astraq alsame yajid lah shhabana balmrsad, yuhrqh wyhlkh. wafi hatayn alaytyn 'ibtal mzaem alsaharat walmshewdhyn, aladhin yddaewn eilm alghyb, wyghrrwn bdeft aleqwl; bkdhbhm waftrayhm"
  72,10,"wanna maeshar aljn- la nelm: ashrrana 'arad allah 'an ynzlh bahl alard, 'am 'arad bihim khyrana whda?"
  72,11,"wana minaa al'abrar almtqwn, waminaa qawm dun dhlk kafaar wfsaq, kunaa frqana wamadhahib mkhtlft"
  72,12,"wana ayqna 'ana allah qadir elyna, wa'anana fi qabdatuh wsltanh, falan nfwth 'iidha 'arad bina amrana 'aynama kna, walan nastatie 'an nuflit min eqabh hrbana 'iilaa alsma', 'iin 'arad bina sw'ana"
  72,13,"w'ina lamaa samiena alquran amnna bh, waqrrna 'anah haqa min eind allh, faman yumin brbh, fa'iinah la yakhshaa nqsanana min hsnath, wala zlmana ylhqh biziadat fi syyath"
  72,14,"wa'anaa minaa alkhadewn lilah baltaet, waminaa aljayrwn alzaalimun aladhin hadu ean tariq alhq, faman 'aslam wakhadae lilah baltaet, fawlyk aladhin qsdu tariq alhaqu walswab, wajthdu fi aikhtiarih fhdahm allah 'ilyh, wa'amaa aljayrwn ean tariq al'islam fakanuu waqwdana ljhnm"
  72,15,"wana minaa alkhadewn lilah baltaet, waminaa aljayrwn alzaalimun aladhin hadu ean tariq alhq, faman 'aslam wakhadae lilah baltaet, fawlyk aladhin qsdu tariq alhaqu walswab, wajthdu fi aikhtiarih fhdahm allah 'ilyh, wa'amaa aljayrwn ean tariq al'islam fakanuu waqwdana ljhnm"
  72,16,"wanh law sar alkufaar min al'iins waljinu ealaa tariqat al'islam, walam yhydu eanha lanzlna ealayhim ma'an kthyrana, wlwssaena ealayhim alrizq fi aldnya; lnkhtbrhm: kayf yashkurun nem allah elyhm? waman yuerd ean taeat rabih wastmae alquran wtdbrh, waleamal bih yudkhilh edhabana shdydana shaqqana"
  72,17,"wanh law sar alkufaar min al'iins waljinu ealaa tariqat al'islam, walam yhydu eanha lanzlna ealayhim ma'an kthyrana, wlwssaena ealayhim alrizq fi aldnya; lnkhtbrhm: kayf yashkurun nem allah elyhm? waman yuerd ean taeat rabih wastmae alquran wtdbrh, waleamal bih yudkhilh edhabana shdydana shaqqana"
  72,18,"wan almasajid lebadt allah whdh, fala taebuduu fiha ghyrh, wa'akhlasuu lah alduea' walebadt fyha; fa'iina almasajid lm tubn 'iilaa lyuebad allh wahdah fyha, dun min swah, wafi hdha wjwb tnzyh almasajid min kl ma yshwb al'iikhlas llh, wamutabaeat rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  72,19,"wanh lamaa qam muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, yaebud rbh, kad aljini yakunun ealayh jamaeat mtrakmt, baeduha fawq bed; min shdt azdhamhm lsmae alquran mnh"
  72,20,"ql -ayha alrswl- lhwla' alkfar: 'iinama 'aebud rabiy whdh, wala 'ushrik maeah fi alebadt ahdana"
  72,21,"qula- 'ayuha alrasula- lahuma: 'iiniy la aqdr 'an 'adfae eankum drana, wala 'ajlib lakum nfeana, qulan: 'iiniy lan yanqidhani min eadhab allah 'ahad 'iin easayatahu, walan 'ajid min dunih malja afrr 'iilayh min eadhabihi, lkn 'amlik 'an 'ubalighukum ean allah ma 'amarani bitablighih lakum, wrsaltah alty 'arsilni biha 'iilaykum. wman yaes allah warasulaha, wyuerd ean din allahi, fa'iina jaza'ah nar jahanam la yakhruj minha abdana"
  72,22,"ql- 'ayuha alrasula- lahuma: 'iiniy la aqdr 'an 'adfae eankum drana, wala 'ajlib lakum nfeana, qulan: 'iiniy lan yanqidhani min eadhab allah 'ahad 'iin easayatahu, walan 'ajid min dunih malja afrr 'iilayh min eadhabihi, lkn 'amlik 'an 'ubalighukum ean allah ma 'amarani bitablighih lakum, wrsaltah alty 'arsilni biha 'iilaykum. wman yaes allah warasulaha, wyuerd ean din allahi, fa'iina jaza'ah nar jahanam la yakhruj minha abdana"
  72,23,"ql- 'ayuha alrasula- lahuma: 'iiniy la aqdr 'an 'adfae eankum drana, wala 'ajlib lakum nfeana, qulan: 'iiniy lan yanqidhani min eadhab allah 'ahad 'iin easayatahu, walan 'ajid min dunih malja afrr 'iilayh min eadhabihi, lkn 'amlik 'an 'ubalighukum ean allah ma 'amarani bitablighih lakum, wrsaltah alty 'arsilni biha 'iilaykum. wman yaes allah warasulaha, wyuerd ean din allahi, fa'iina jaza'ah nar jahanam la yakhruj minha abdana"
  72,24,"hta 'iidha 'absar almushrikun ma yueadun bih min aleadhabi, fasayaelamun eind hululih bihima: man 'adeaf nasrana wmeynana wa'aqul jndana?"
  72,25,"qul -ayha alrswl- lhwla' almshrkyn: ma 'adri ahdha aleadhab aldhy wuedtm bih qarib zmnh, 'am yajeal lah rabiy mdt twyl? wahu subhanah ealam bima ghab ean alabsar, fala yuzhir ealaa ghaybih ahdana min khlqh, 'iilaa man aikhtarah allah lrsalth wartdah, fa'iinah yutlehm ealaa bed alghyb, wayursil min 'amam alrasul wamin khalfih malayikat yahfazunah min aljn; lialaa ystrqwh wyhmsu bih 'iilaa alkhnt; liaelam alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm, 'ana alrusul qablih kanuu ealaa mthl halh min altabligh bialhaqi walsdq, wa'anah hufz kama hufzu min aljn, wa'ana allah subhanah 'ahat ealamah bima eindahum zahrana wbatnana min alshraye walahkam wghyrha, la yfwth minha shy', wa'anah taealaa ahsa kula shay' eddana, falam yakhf ealayh minh shy'"
  72,26,"ql -ayha alrswl- lhwla' almshrkyn: ma 'adri ahdha aleadhab aldhy wuedtm bih qarib zmnh, 'am yajeal lah rabiy mdt twyl? wahu subhanah ealam bima ghab ean alabsar, fala yuzhir ealaa ghaybih ahdana min khlqh, 'iilaa man aikhtarah allah lrsalth wartdah, fa'iinah yutlehm ealaa bed alghyb, wayursil min 'amam alrasul wamin khalfih malayikat yahfazunah min aljn; lialaa ystrqwh wyhmsu bih 'iilaa alkhnt; liaelam alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm, 'ana alrusul qablih kanuu ealaa mthl halh min altabligh bialhaqi walsdq, wa'anah hufz kama hufzu min aljn, wa'ana allah subhanah 'ahat ealamah bima eindahum zahrana wbatnana min alshraye walahkam wghyrha, la yfwth minha shy', wa'anah taealaa ahsa kula shay' eddana, falam yakhf ealayh minh shy'"
  72,27,"qul -ayha alrswl- lhwla' almshrkyn: ma 'adri ahdha aleadhab aldhy wuedtm bih qarib zmnh, 'am yajeal lah rabiy mdt twyl? wahu subhanah ealam bima ghab ean alabsar, fala yuzhir ealaa ghaybih ahdana min khlqh, 'iilaa man aikhtarah allah lrsalth wartdah, fa'iinah yutlehm ealaa bed alghyb, wayursil min 'amam alrasul wamin khalfih malayikat yahfazunah min aljn; lialaa ystrqwh wyhmsu bih 'iilaa alkhnt; liaelam alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm, 'ana alrusul qablih kanuu ealaa mthl halh min altabligh bialhaqi walsdq, wa'anah hufz kama hufzu min aljn, wa'ana allah subhanah 'ahat ealamah bima eindahum zahrana wbatnana min alshraye walahkam wghyrha, la yfwth minha shy', wa'anah taealaa ahsa kula shay' eddana, falam yakhf ealayh minh shy'"
  72,28,"ql -ayha alrswl- lhwla' almshrkyn: ma 'adri ahdha aleadhab aldhy wuedtm bih qarib zmnh, 'am yajeal lah rabiy mdt twyl? wahu subhanah ealam bima ghab ean alabsar, fala yuzhir ealaa ghaybih ahdana min khlqh, 'iilaa man aikhtarah allah lrsalth wartdah, fa'iinah yutlehm ealaa bed alghyb, wayursil min 'amam alrasul wamin khalfih malayikat yahfazunah min aljn; lialaa ystrqwh wyhmsu bih 'iilaa alkhnt; liaelam alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm, 'ana alrusul qablih kanuu ealaa mthl halh min altabligh bialhaqi walsdq, wa'anah hufz kama hufzu min aljn, wa'ana allah subhanah 'ahat ealamah bima eindahum zahrana wbatnana min alshraye walahkam wghyrha, la yfwth minha shy', wa'anah taealaa ahsa kula shay' eddana, falam yakhf ealayh minh shy'"
  73,1,"ya 'ayuha almtghty bthyabh, qum lilsalat fi allayl 'iilaa ysyrana mnh. qum nsf allayl 'aw anqus min alnisf qalilana hataa tasil 'iilaa althlth, 'aw zid ealaa alnisf hataa tasil 'iilaa althlthyn, waiqra alquran btuadat wtmhhul mbyinana alhrwf walwqwf"
  73,2,"ya 'ayuha almtghty bthyabh, qum lilsalat fi allayl 'iilaa ysyrana mnh. qum nsf allayl 'aw anqus min alnisf qalilana hataa tasil 'iilaa althlth, 'aw zid ealaa alnisf hataa tasil 'iilaa althlthyn, waiqra alquran btuadat wtmhhul mbyinana alhrwf walwqwf"
  73,3,"ya 'ayuha almtghty bthyabh, qum lilsalat fi allayl 'iilaa ysyrana mnh. qum nsf allayl 'aw anqus min alnisf qalilana hataa tasil 'iilaa althlth, 'aw zid ealaa alnisf hataa tasil 'iilaa althlthyn, waiqra alquran btuadat wtmhhul mbyinana alhrwf walwqwf"
  73,4,"ya 'ayuha almtghty bthyabh, qum lilsalat fi allayl 'iilaa ysyrana mnh. qum nsf allayl 'aw anqus min alnisf qalilana hataa tasil 'iilaa althlth, 'aw zid ealaa alnisf hataa tasil 'iilaa althlthyn, waiqra alquran btuadat wtmhhul mbyinana alhrwf walwqwf"
  73,5,'ina snnzl ealayk -ayha alnby- qranana ezymana mshtmla ealaa al'awamir walnwahy walahkam alshreyt
  73,6,"'in alebadt alty tnsha fi jwf allayl hi 'ashadu tathyrana fi alqlb, wabyn qawlana lfragh alqalb min mshaghl aldnya"
  73,7,"'in lak fi alnahar tsrfana wtqlbana fi msalhk, washtghala waseana bamwr alrsalt, ffrrigh nafsak laylana lebadt rbk"
  73,8,"wadhkr -ayha alnby- aism rbk, fadeh bh, wanqte 'iilayh anqtaeana tamana fi ebadtk, watawakal elyh. hu malik almashriq walmaghrib la mebwd bihaqi 'iilaa hw, faetmd elyh, wfwwid amwrk 'ilyh"
  73,9,"wadhkr -ayha alnby- aism rbk, fadeh bh, wanqte 'iilayh anqtaeana tamana fi ebadtk, watawakal elyh. hu malik almashriq walmaghrib la mebwd bihaqi 'iilaa hw, faetmd elyh, wfwwid amwrk 'ilyh"
  73,10,"wasbr ealaa ma yaquluh almushrikun fyk wafi dynk, wkhalfhm fi afealhm albatlt, mae al'ierad enhm, wtrk alantqam mnhm"
  73,11,"deny -ayha alrswl- whwla' almukadhibin biayati 'ashab alnaeim waltrf fi aldnya, wmhhilhm zmnana qalilana btakhyr aleadhab eanhum hataa yablugh alkitab 'ajalah bedhabhm"
  73,12,"'iina lahum eindana fi alakhirat qywdana thaqilat wnarana mstert yuhrqwn bha, wteamana kryhana ynshab fi alhlwq la ystsagh, wedhabana mwjeana"
  73,13,"'in lahum eindana fi alakhirat qywdana thaqilat wnarana mstert yuhrqwn bha, wteamana kryhana ynshab fi alhlwq la ystsagh, wedhabana mwjeana"
  73,14,"ywm tdtrb al'ard waljibal wttzlzl hataa tasir aljibal tala min alraml sayilaan mtnathrana, baed 'an kanat sulbt jamdt"
  73,15,"'ina 'arsalna 'ilykm- ya 'ahl \"mk\"- mhmdana rasulana shahdana ealaykum bima sadar minkum min alkufr walesyan, kama 'arsalna musaa rasulana 'iilaa alttaghiat frewn, fkdhdhab fireawn bmwsa, walam yumin brsalth, wesa amrh, fahlknah 'ihlakana shdydana. wafi hdha tahdhir min mesyt alrasul mhmd, salaa allah ealayh wslm; khashyat 'ana yusib aleasy mithl ma 'asab fireawn wqwmh"
  73,16,"'ina 'arsalna 'ilykm- ya 'ahl \"mk\"- mhmdana rasulana shahdana ealaykum bima sadar minkum min alkufr walesyan, kama 'arsalna musaa rasulana 'iilaa alttaghiat frewn, fkdhdhab fireawn bmwsa, walam yumin brsalth, wesa amrh, fahlknah 'ihlakana shdydana. wafi hdha tahdhir min mesyt alrasul mhmd, salaa allah ealayh wslm; khashyat 'ana yusib aleasy mithl ma 'asab fireawn wqwmh"
  73,17,fkyf taqun anfskm- 'iina kfrtm- eadhab yawm alqiamat aldhy yshyb fih alwildan alsghar; min shdt hwlh wkrbh?
  73,18,"alsma' mtsdet fi dhalik alywm; lshdt hwlh, kan waed allah taealaa bmjy' dhlk alyawm waqeana la mhalt"
  73,19,"'in hadhih alayat almkhwft alty fiha alqware walzwajr ezt webrt llnas, faman 'arad alateaz walantfae biha atakhadh alttaeat waltqwa tryqana tawasalah 'iilaa ridwan rabih aldhy khalaqah wrbbah"